e.org/web/20170823075223/http://www.slate.com/articles/video/video/2014/08/_zombie_star_hubble_spots_star_sn_2012z_living_after_supernova.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Hauk">{{cite web|url=http://time.com/3086831/nasa-hubble-supernova-zombie-star/|title=Hubble Finds Supernova Star System Linked to Potential "Zombie Star"|first1=Alexis|last1=Hauk|work=[[Time_Magazine|Time Magazine]]|date=6 August 2014|accessdate=30 October 2014|archive-date=2016-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318201934/http://time.com/3086831/nasa-hubble-supernova-zombie-star/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Iax超新星類似Ia超新星，但是它的噴發物速度較低，光度也較暗淡<ref name="McCully">{{cite journal |url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v512/n7512/full/nature13615.html |title=A luminous, blue progenitor system for the Type Iax supernova 2012Z |first1=Curtis |last1=McCully |first2=Saurabh W. |last2=Jha |first3=Ryan J. |last3=Foley |first4=Lars |last4=Bildsten |first5=Wen-fai |last5=Fong |first6=Robert P. |last6=Kirshner |first7=G. H. |last7=Marion |first8=Adam G. |last8=Riess |first9=Maximilian D. |last9=Stritzinger |journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] |doi=10.1038/nature13615 |number=512 |pages=54–56 |date=7 August 2014 |accessdate=30 October 2014 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517181129/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature13615 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科學家認為Iax超新星約佔Ia超新星的5%至30%。已有30顆超新星屬於此一類別<ref name="Post">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2014/08/06/astronomers-may-have-found-a-new-zombie-star/|first1=Rachel|last1=Feltman|title=Astronomers may have found a new zombie star|work=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|accessdate=30 October 2014|archive-date=2020-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603194345/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2014/08/06/astronomers-may-have-found-a-new-zombie-star/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

